#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/basics.rst:127
msgid "Short name"
msgstr "Kratak naziv"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/basics.rst:129
msgid ""
"A number of elements have both a **short name** and a **title**. The short "
"name is a text string used for machine-to-machine communication while the "
"title is for the benefit of humans. For example, a dataset might have the "
"descriptive title *“Maximum Atmospheric Temperature”* and be requested using"
" the abbreviated short name *“ATMAX”*. You can set title, short name and "
"abstract for:"
msgstr ""
"Više elemenata ima i **kratak naziv** i **naslov**. Kratak naziv je "
"tekstualna niska koja se koristi za komunikaciju mašina-mašina, dok je "
"naslov za potrebe ljudi. Na primer, skup podataka može imati opisni naslov "
"*„Maksimalna temperatura atmosfere“* i biti zahtevan pomoću skraćenog "
"kratkog naziva *„ATMAX“*. Naslov, kratak naziv i apstrakt možete postaviti "
"za:"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/basics.rst:136
msgid ""
"**Layers**: right-click on a layer and choose :menuselection:`Properties... "
"--> QGIS Server --> Description`."
msgstr ""
"**Slojeve**: kliknite desnim tasterom na sloj i izaberite "
":menuselection:`Svojstva... --> QGIS Server --> Opis`."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/basics.rst:139
msgid ""
"**Groups**: right-click on a group and select :guilabel:`Set Group WMS data`"
msgstr ""
"**Grupe**: kliknite desnim tasterom na grupu i izaberite :guilabel:`Postavi "
"WMS podatke grupe`"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/services/basics.rst:141
msgid ""
"**Project**: go to :menuselection:`Project --> Properties... --> QGIS Server"
" --> Service Capabilities`."
msgstr ""
"**Projekat**: idite na :menuselection:`Projekat --> Svojstva... --> QGIS "
"Server --> Mogućnosti servisa`."

